org.usfirst.frc.team3997.robot

Class MasterController

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.usfirst.frc.team3997.robot.MasterController

  • public class MasterController
extends java.lang.Object
    Getter and setter class that packages important classes for autonomous. e.g master.getRobotModel() returns the RobotModel class passed in Robot.java
    Author:
    Peter I. Chacko, Eric Warner, John Sullivan Jr, Jake Boothby, Elliot Friedlander
